data.name: Label3.Text
data.value:
At the top of the 'System' tab there are different options to choose from, these are as follows:
1. End Process - End an already running process. 2. Run - Create a new process. 3. Resource Monitor - View a detailed version of Task Manager. 4. Control Panel - Change the settings of your system. 5. Task Manager - Check the performance of your system. 6. Registry Editor - Edit the registry of Windows. 7. Windows Version - Show the Windows version information dialogue. 8. Windows Explorer - Access all of the files on your computer, this will also allow you to get to the Windows taskbar. 9. Power - Choose a power option for your system to perform.
